First edition of the Ox Collection created with the purpose of exploring with geometric forms and emotions. How can we achieve new ways to interact with the human mind and the digital world?

Series 1/200

Every drop the supply will decrease by 9 editions until reaching 1/2

Perks of being a holder:

Digital 3D File ready to import on a metaverse space.

Access to retrieve a psychical piece created specially for you.

Presale access to mint the upcoming Humo Studio furniture collections.
